  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9? \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What are the consequences of Sri Lanka Electricity Board's delay in increasing rates? Central Bank Governor Explanation",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Central Bank Governor Nandalal Weerasinghe said that Sri Lanka Electricity Board's delay in tariff increase has affected the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation and the country's monetary policy.",
        "He mentioned that although the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has started operating on the basis of price formula, the electricity board has delayed the rate increase, but the cash inflow for the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has been affected. They do not have rupees to buy dollars.",
        "Because of this, they are demanding money from the treasury and because of this, they are asking the central bank to print money, the central bank governor said.",
        "Nandalal Weerasinghe has said that the Sri Lanka Electricity Board is facing shortages but it has been delayed in increasing its tariffs, and although the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation is selling oil, it is not getting enough rupees from the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "The Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has requested 217 billion rupees from the treasury, so they are asking the Central Bank."
      ],
